  <li>https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=473105</li>
  <li>https://forum.startcom.org/viewtopic.php?p=21707#p21707</li>
  <li>http://serverfault.com/questions/684736/why-does-chrome-on-1-computer-say-my-certificate-is-invalid-insecure</li>
</ul>

